  "title": "Numbers and Letters",
  "description": "This dataset contains neuroimaging data from an experiment investigating the neural processing of numbers, letters, and false fonts presented as single items or strings. The study employs event-related experimental design with two runs, each utilizing distinct stimulus categories marked by specific trigger codes to enable precise temporal analysis of brain responses to different visual stimuli. Data were acquired using magnetoencephalography (MEG).",
